column1: List of known kinase-substrate and phosphatase-substrate pairs for which the EMAP contained interaction scores.
The kinase (or phosphatase) is listed in column A/B, the substrates are listed in column C/D, and the genetic interaction score is listed in column E
In this analysis we also included kinase or phosphatase regulatory proteins (such as the cyclins, for example).
The kinase (or phosphatase) regulators are listed in column A/B, the substrates are listed in column C/D, and the genetic interaction score is listed in column E
